@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rxesev(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = 0.27
    v1 = (0.38 - 0.32)
    tmp = wp.exp(tmp)
    v1 = (wp.sin((v1 + 0.18 + v2 + 0.18)) - (v0 + 0.94))
    v0 = wp.cos((wp.exp(v0 + 0.53) - (v0 + 0.09 - v0 + 0.04)))
    v2 = ((0.83 - (v0 + 0.95 / v0 + 0.41)) - wp.cos(wp.sin(tmp + 0.64)))
    v0 = ((wp.exp(tmp + 0.67) * wp.exp(v0 + 0.95)) + ((v2 + 0.80 / tmp + 0.58) * (v1 + 0.93 * tmp + 0.05)))
    data[tid] = v0
